comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of GSW possession was upheld.
Dellavedova (MIL) and Curry (GSW) make incidental contact that does not affect Curry's FOM off ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Green (GSW) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot
Parker (MIL) and Durant (GSW) make incidental contact.
[Detectable with stop watch] Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Iguodala (GSW) sets the screen on Dellavedova (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) and Green (GSW) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Iguodala (GSW) sets the screen on Dellavedova (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RATR shows Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with the ball on Green's (GSW) shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) make incidental contact that does not affect Antetokounmpo's FOM off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves his pivot foot.
Teletovic (MIL) sets the screen on Iguodala (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Thompson (GSW) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with Green (GSW) that does not affect Green's FOM off ball.
Green (GSW) sets the screen on Parker (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Green (GSW) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Green (GSW) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his ability to post.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes body to body contact with Thompson (GSW) that affects his SQBR.
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his SQBR on the drive.
Green (GSW) makes contact to the arm and hand of Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Pachulia (GSW) and Plumlee (MIL) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Green (GSW) legally contests Antetokounmpo's (MIL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
